gomodel:SYNGO_1458  a     owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Automated change 2024-03-14: GO:0099055 replaced by GO:0045211" , "Rationale: Immuno EM of 5-HT3A receptor\n\n8/9/2017 Pim\n- Based on the known transmembrane topology of the protein, the \"integral component of ... membrane\" term was chosen.\n- literal: \"A dendritic spine with a dense immunolabelling at the level of a synaptic differentiation illustrates the typical postsynaptic ultrastructural distribution of immunostaining within the pyramidal cell layer (CA1) of the hippocampus (E)\". Experimental description: Animals\nAdult male Wistar rats, weighing 300±350 g, were maintained under controlled environmental conditions (21 +/- 1 °C, 60% relative humidity, 12-h light : 12-h dark cycle, food and water available ad libitum)." ;
        lego:modelstate   "production" ;
        dc:contributor    "https://orcid.org/0000-0001-9425-2935" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-2514-0216" ;
        dc:date           "2024-03-14" ;
